data.description: Nestled in the serene Palmetto Oaks Subdivision of Palmetto, GA, this newly built home is a beacon of comfort and style. This impressive residence boasts four bedrooms and three full baths across two stories, with all bedrooms situated upstairs for enhanced privacy. The main level features a versatile flex room, perfect for a bedroom on main, formal dining room, living area, or office space, complemented by a nearby full bathroom. The home includes a luxurious bathroom with an incredible soaking tub, and walk-in closets, as well as a full, unfinished basement ready for your personal touch. Smart home features, LED lighting, and energy-efficient appliances ensure a seamless blend of luxury and practicality. Positioned on a cul-de-sac lot, this property offers a tranquil setting with easy access to major highways, shopping, and dining.
